  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501968248\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" width=\"1800\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=68091038&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QOehQEaiayFZ3A0xRGS3cy4Xvj4qqW9Um7Yq6gibs4XxQZJUKNpLHRBQiaIhNM9LDJicSL9noSje1gibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"padding:16px 20px;color:rgb(80, 80, 80);visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:18px;border-color:initial;line-height:1.64;box-sizing:border-box !important;quotes:none;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:4px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:20px;border-width:initial;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:20px;border-style:none;\">\n   <p style=\"max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;visibility: visible;text-align: left;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">「有意思小周刊」是我利用零碎时间，梳理记录一周的日常阅读与思考内容。目的是为以后更好构建自己知识体系，也为了将这些内容分享给你。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">以下是这期值得关注的内容</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">📰 推荐阅读</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">1. 一文搞懂分期支付，花呗白条背后的小秘密</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">2. B端产品经理如何学习AI</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">3. 离开大厂后，我花两年时间，救活了自己</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">4. 很多大厂主按钮故意不用主题色，什么原因？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">5. 《智能体设计模式》之多智能体协作模式：分工协同突破单一智能体能力边界</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">6. 千万级大表如何删除数据？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">7. 大模型音频水印技术：用AI守护音频数据的“身份指纹”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">8. 对李想的第二次3小时访谈：智慧是我们和万物的关系</span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🔎&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">发现新大陆</span></strong></span></h4>\n  <p style=\"marg